plot: Evangelical video in which Claudio, a womanizer, contracts AIDS due to his promiscuous lifestyle, and, in the hospital, meets Mauricio, a homosexual Evangelist who is also infected and will discover Jesus to Claudio.
title: S.I.D.A., síndrome de muerte
